data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom Plantation home, conveniently located near 595 for an easy commute and close to Seminole Middle School and Tropical Elementary School. Inside, an updated kitchen and island providing ample space for eating and socializing. Additionally, the formal dining room area offers an elegant space for entertaining and family meals. The full impact front doors and windows enhance security and energy efficiency. As an added bonus, the seller is gifting a home warranty that's valid until January 9th, 2025. Step outside to discover a unique feature: a wall for a projector screen, perfect for movie nights by the pool and patio. Don't miss the chance to make this your new home!
